00:00:39.110 --> 00:00:43.136
counts as 3 for him. So, it's almost as if we're taking this 3 and a 3rd and

00:00:43.136 --> 00:00:47.610
rounding it down to the nearest integer, 3. So, let's say that x equals the

00:00:47.610 --> 00:00:52.144
actual number of packs of nozzles we have. So, for example in this case, we

