00:01:08.422 --> 00:01:13.849
also known as the Greatest Integer Function. The notation for the equation is

00:01:13.849 --> 00:01:18.137
this, y equals x inside these double square brackets, which basically means

00:01:18.137 --> 00:01:22.358
that the y value is equal to the greatest integer that is less than or equal to

00:01:22.358 --> 00:01:28.557
